      "created_at": "2025-01-02T14:59:00.252Z",
      "cooked": "<p>My old eyes suck too!!! <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">  We will see what we can do.  You can also use our broadcast feature and open it up on a web page. Just turn it on in settings in the app and open your personal URL provided on the website and in the app.</p>\n<p>See the app in front of the broadcast page.  The broadcast page has much bigger numbers.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/24c9db1a8a6f28fa97aec4397bf675f640527770.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/24c9db1a8a6f28fa97aec4397bf675f640527770\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/24c9db1a8a6f28fa97aec4397bf675f640527770_2_690x447.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"5frF79tdauN8cz9NOilT6xLgOuk\" width=\"690\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/24c9db1a8a6f28fa97aec4397bf675f640527770_2_690x447.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/24c9db1a8a6f28fa97aec4397bf675f640527770_2_1035x670.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/24c9db1a8a6f28fa97aec4397bf675f640527770_2_1380x894.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"21232F\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d71245 64.9 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
